--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
>>  Make SSL certificates with certbot:

    >   Install certbot:
    
        # add-apt-repository ppa:certbot/certbot
        # apt-get update
        # apt-get install -y certbot

    >   Create certificates:
    
        # certbot certonly
    
    >   Renew all certificates:
    
        # certbot renew --dry-run

